om\": 263, \"to\": 288}, {\"ngram\": \"fellow skateboarding legend Tony Hawk\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macdonald went pro in 1994 and is decades older than his fellowTeam Great Britain skateboarders, 16-year-olds Sky Brown and Lola Tambling.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998007002947429, \"rank\": 0.00019544647199297086, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sky Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\"}, {\"begin\": 548, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lola_Cars\", \"score\": 0.999995970338593, \"rank\": 4.02914617194674e-06, \"text\": \"Lola\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lola_Cars\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lola_Cars\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Macdonald\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macdonald, a 23-time X Games champion, zipped through the skatepark during the preliminaries Wednesday, showing off flashy moves including a madonna and a body varial 540.\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Macdonald\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"a 23-time X Games champion\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"the skatepark\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"the preliminaries\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"flashy moves\", \