1127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was getting like, four hours of sleep because I was up in the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4773610510668133e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four hours\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I bought an electric skateboard so I was just zooming around, just like meeting everybody,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an electric skateboard\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a really beautiful thing to be a part of; just being here, being an Olympian,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999932124142816, \"rank\": 6.78763172108498e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really beautiful thing\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then today was even more special.\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like the icing on the cake that I got to be here and participate.\\\"\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the icing\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"the cake\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Skateboarding is arelatively new sport at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new sport\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It debuted in 2021 at the Tokyo Summer Games and has already been approved for the Los Angeles Games in 2028,per NBC Olympics.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999899525847, \"rank\": 9.940997401161125e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1694, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Summer Games\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macdonald first hinted at his plans to compete in an Olympics in an August 2022 poston Instagram.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1796, \"end\": 1805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3053123563494618e-21, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Macdonald\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"his plans\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete, who was born and raised just outside Boston, Massachusetts, and holds dual citizenship because of his English-born father, revealed at the time that he qualified forGreat Britain's national skateboard park team.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1866, \"end\": 1879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massachusetts\", \"score\": 0.9999938122085037, \"rank\": 2.2776982808860997e-06, \"text\": \"Massachusetts\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massachusetts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massachusetts\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athlete\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1819}, {\"ngram\": \"Boston\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"dual citizenship\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"his English-born father\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"Britain's national skateboard park team\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hawk, who clapped for his former vert doubles partner at Wednesday's event, told Olympic organizers he was \\\"proud\\\" of Macdonald - but hardly surprised by his tenacity.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hawk\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"his former vert doubles partner\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday's event\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic organizers\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2133}, {\"ngram\": \"Macdonald\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"his tenacity\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Andy is a prime example of how much discipline can pay off,\\\" he said, adding, \\\"You can always count on him to do something amazing.\\\"\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Andy\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"a prime example\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"how much discipline\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"fr